title: Acer Recovery Management
description:
This is from a Acer ES1-711-P1UV Laptop. Not sure if it will work with other Acer laptops but worth a try.

Can't believe Acer charges $40 for this when they should let you dowload for free since you bought the laptop. 

I searched everywhere for this because I had to replace my HDD before i remembered I made a backup which i had stored on a file server. 

Hope this works for you and saves you $$$ enjoy!!!
